Interface ObjectsModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    ObjectsModelImpl

    public interface ObjectsModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Objects Model'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Service Providers
    • Work Items
    • Governance Strategies
